	("/*"): New rule to test whether we should treat /*
	as a single token or as two tokens.
	(<COMMENTC>.): New rule to skip a character.
	(<COMMENTC>\n.*): New rule to consume the line.
	(<COMMENTC>"*/"): New rule to call endOfCComment.

